---
title: Modules &raquo; m_alltime
layout: default
---

## Description	

Provides an `/ALLTIME` command to get the current time on all servers.

## Configuration Tags

This module does not require any extra configuration, other than the
`<module>` tag to load it. 

## Commands

`/ALLTIME`

Returns the current time in UTC on every server.

## User Modes

This module does not implement any user modes.

## Channel Modes

This module does not implement any channel modes.

## Extended Bans

This module does not implement any extended bans.

##

This command is oper-only.
